  "prompt": "What is the fee structure of Sri Chaitanya Visakhapatnam?",
  "response": "The fee structure for Sri Chaitanya schools and colleges, including those in Visakhapatnam, can vary based on factors such as the type of program (school or college), grade level, and any additional services offered (like hostel facilities, coaching, etc.). Typically, these institutions charge a combination of tuition fees, registration fees, and other miscellaneous charges.\n\nFor the most accurate and updated information regarding the fee structure, it is best to visit the official Sri Chaitanya website or contact the administration office of the specific branch in Visakhapatnam directly.",
